# Bouncing Balls

Set up the environment
  #ball = [x: 0 y: 0 vx: 1 vy: 0 ]
  #system/timer = [resolution: 100]
  #gravity = 98
  #boundary = 5000

## Update Condition

The positions of the balls update on every tick
  ~ #system/timer.tick
  #ball.x := #ball.x + #ball.vx
  #ball.y := #ball.y + #ball.vy
  #ball.vy := #ball.vy + #gravity

## Boundary Conditions

Constrain balls to within the boundary 
  iy = #ball.y > #boundary
  y[iy] := #boundary
  #ball.vy[iy] := 0 - 1 * vy * 90 / 100

## Reset on click

  ~ click = [#html/event/click]
  [#ball x y]
  x := click.x
  y := click.y